### US226 — Parts Inventory & Low-Stock Alerts (Maintenance Supervisor)

### 1. Login as Maintenance Supervisor
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "supervisor@airline.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("token", response.body.token);
%}

###

### 2. View all parts usage inventory
GET http://localhost:8080/api/maintenance/parts/inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Get low-stock alerts with default threshold (10 units)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/maintenance/parts/low-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Get low-stock alerts with custom threshold (5 units)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/maintenance/parts/low-stock?threshold=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
